  ('optician-moex-02125', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '患者一眼未矯正前視力0.3，使用+2.00 D透鏡可使視力達到1.0，加到+2.75 D時，視力仍維持1.0，而用 +3.00 D 時視力下降至0.8，下列敘述何者正確？', '["顯性遠視（manifest hyperopia）是+2.00 D", "絕對遠視（absolute hyperopia）是+1.00 D", "機能遠視（facultative hyperopia）是+0.75 D", "隱性遠視（latent hyperopia）是+2.75 D"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "881ca37171e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f8c58b11cf7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02126', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個+2.00 D的薄透鏡和一個+6.00 D的兩同軸薄透鏡若緊密相貼在一起，一個物體放在這個系統前50 cm 的位置，求成像的位置與性質？', '["在第二透鏡後側+16.7 cm實像", "在第二透鏡後側+16.7 cm虛像", "在第二透鏡後側+13.3 cm實像", "在第二透鏡後側+13.3 cm虛像"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "881ca37171e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f8c58b11cf7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
